	<string name="whats_new">
        <![CDATA[
            <b>What\'s new in version 1.5.2</b><br>
			<p>News you\'re listening to can be shared now via plugins to their social networks. Just swipe up the picture!</p>
			<p>Fixed bug with spontaneous playback resume.</p>
			<p>Settings to setup reading speed is now available at the Settings.</p>
			<p>Select the whole newsfeed tree is now restricted to a single source branch.</p>
			<p>There is no «Stop» anymore – only «Pause».</p>
			<p>Huge speedup of the sources list displaying and managing.</p>
			<p>Links at the news are now clickable.</p>
			<b>What\'s new in version 1.4.8</b><br>
			<p>Application was redesigned</p>
			<p>Added side-menu with fast plugin switches (in case you want to restrict receiving some news).</p>
			<p>Added «List mode» for the moments, when user can safely read the screen. «Music only» player mode activated automatically upon switch.</p>
			<p>Added the ability to share any URL to the app to make user able to listen to any text, published at the web.</p>
			<p>Changed all the way the application is getting news. Now it is faster a lot.</p>
			<p>Changed the notification widget. Now it is a little more useable.</p>
			<p>Some app modules were rewritten from scratch. Now they’re more stable and fast.</p>
			<p>A lot of bug-fixes.</p>	        
			<b>What\'s new in version 1.4.4</b><br>		
			<p>Google speech engine was enabled to use with Speind. All Google-supported languages are available now to be used for listening to news.</p>
			<p>All premium voices are the the subject for purchase in app from the current moment.</p>
			<p>Some changes were made to the speech logic. </p>
			<p>Smart-pause implemented to make return to listening to the app from the incoming call more comfortable.</p>
			<p>Some minor but very useful interface changes.</p>
			<p>A lot of bug-fixes and improvements in the core code.</p>
			<b>What\'s new in version 1.3.9</b><br>
			<p>Fixed issue with the Google ART runtime</p>
			<p>Fixed the wrong progress bar display under Android versions 4.4+</p>
			<p>Fixed the general failure error when quitting app during music playback</p>
			<p>Fixed some minor bugs.</p>
			<b>What\'s new in version 1.3.8</b><br>
			<p>Small changes in user interface.</p>
			<p>Fixed some minor bugs.</p>
			<b>What\'s new in version 1.3.6</b><br>
			<p>Added French language and newsfeeds for France and Canada.</p>
			<p>Added "Smart-pause" - now application will continue reading an article instead of starting over.</p>
			<p>Added this "What\'s new" screen.</p>
			<b>What\'s new in version 1.3.5</b><br>
			<p>Added an option, preventing screen switch off. It is very useful to have one-touch control over the app when you\'re on the track or driving.</p>
			<p>Added and option to add custom RSS-sources. Very handy to keep informed with the feeds that you are interested in, but we don\'t know about them</p>
			<p>Added voices to the shop. Now you can change the voice that read news to you.</p>
			<p>Fixed some minor bugs. Added some new.</p>
		]]>	
	</string>
